{{Infobox museum | name = Bolivia Municipal Museum | native_name = Museo Municipal de Bolivia | native_name_lang = Spanish | image = | imagesize = | caption = | coordinates = | established = {{Start date|1982|12|27|df=y}} | location = [[Bolivia, Cuba|Bolivia]], [[Cuba]] | website = <!-- {{URL|example.com}} --> }} '''Bolivia Municipal Museum''' is a [[museum]] located in [[Bolivia, Cuba|Bolivia]], [[Cuba]]. It was established on 27 December 1982.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.cnpc.cult.cu/institucion/557|title=Museo Municipal de Bolivia|publisher=Portal del Consejo Nacional de Patrimonio Cultural|accessdate=2015-11-01}}</ref>
The museum holds collections on history, archeology, natural science and decorative arts.
