 You See Me]]'' and [[Sofia Coppola]]'s ''[[The Bling Ring]]''. * {{cite journal |author=Denby, David |authormask=1 |date=August 5, 2013 |title=Young and restless |department=The Critics. The Current Cinema |journal=The New Yorker |volume=89 |issue=23 |pages=78-79 |url=http://www.newyorker.com/magazine/2013/08/05/young-and-restless-2 |<!--accessdate=2016-12-20-->}} [[James Ponsoldt]]'s ''The Spectacular Now'', [[Maggie Carey]]'s ''The To Do List'' and [[Paul Schrader]]'s ''The Canyons''. * {{cite journal |author=Denby, David |authormask=1 |date=October 21, 2013 |title=Fighting to survive |department=The Critics. The Current Cinema |journal=The New Yorker |volume=89 |issue=33 |pages=108-109 |url=http://www.newyorker.com/magazine/2013/10/21/fighting-to-survive-2 |<!--accessdate=2017-06-12-->}} Reviews [[Steve McQueen (director)|Steve McQueen]]'s ''[[12 Years a Slave (film)|12 Years a Slave]]'' and [[J. C. Chandor]]'s ''[[All is Lost]]''. * {{cite journal |author=Denby, David |authormask=1 |date=November 4, 2013 |title=Getting serious |department=The Critics. The Current Cinema |journal=The New Yorker |volume=89 |issue=35 |pages=116-117 |url=https://www.newyorker.com/magazine/2013/11/04/getting-serious-2 |<!--accessdate=2017-10-20-->}} Discusses [[Matthew McConaughey]] in [[Jean-Marc Vallée]]'s ''[[Dallas Buyers Club]]'' (2013). * {{cite journal |author=Denby, David |authormask=1 |date=December 2, 2013 |title=Winners and losers |department=The Critics. The Current Cinema |journal=The New Yorker |volume=89 |issue=39 |pages=66-68 |url=http://www.newyorker.com/magazine/2013/12/02/winners-and-losers-2 |<!--accessdate=2017-07-08-->}} Reviews [[Francis Lawrence]]'s ''[[The Hunger Games: Catching Fire]]'' and [[Alex Gibney]]'s ''[[The Armstrong Lie]]''. * {{cite journal |author=Denby, David |authormask=1 |date=December 16, 2013 |title=Grand scam |department=The Critics. The Current Cinema |journal=The New Yorker |volume=89 |issue=41 |pages=80-82 |url=https://www.newyorker.com